'''Gerard Delanty''' (born 1960) is a British sociologist and Professor of [[Sociology]] and Social & Political Thought at the [[University of Sussex]].<ref>[http://www.eurozine.com/authors/delanty.html About Gerard Delanty]</ref>
He is also the editor of [[European Journal of Social Theory]].
<ref>[http://est.sagepub.com/ European Journal of Social Theory]</ref>

